{"tid":282694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集：回歸廿周年系列一之這麼近 那麼遠","createTime":"2017-06-13T14:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T12:30:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"247af1f0afb1ccf86337d22ec3a3b9e9b69db8b6","tid":282694,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xhpC8H9LOww#t=46.260233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxhpC8H9LOww%23t%3D46.260233&d=J9oVfvWgaPX5x2D7PFKzrsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=39c67e64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xhpC8H9LOww#t=46.260233</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年6月12日<br />\n廿年來中港兩地經濟、生活、文化迅速融合，亦因此產生磨擦和紛爭，兩地生活文化大不同，經過廿年後，矛盾更激烈。有人著重保留兩地的邊界，透過拍攝照片，希望保留邊界以南的香港特色不變；也有人早早北上發展，尋求機遇。廿年來，香港和香港人都不停尋找自己的定位。"},{"pid":"dac042eed3dfff5ae61b5f2f971a20ad4bf7a0d9","tid":282694,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T20:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cb6b21fc06abc3be442aa7a33bf0e891931ec4","tid":282694,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}